<section class="section section--tint sr-prose">
  <div class="container--narrow">
    <h2 class="sr-prose__heading">Return &amp; Exchange Policy</h2>
    <p>All sales are final. Due to Covid19 outbreak - we are unable to do exchanges or returns on all products sold by Menon Regenerative Institute (Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness).</p>
    <p>We only accept returns or exchanges, if the incorrect item was shipped to you. However, these products must be unopened, unused and returned in their original packaging.</p>
    <p>If the products returned are damaged, opened, or not returned in their original packaging, no refund will be issued.</p>
    <p>Refunds, returns or exchanges for incorrect items shipped are processed within 14 business days after the items are returned and received by Menon Regenerative Institute (Menon Medispa &amp; Wellness).</p>
    <p>Return address:</p>
    <p>
      Menon Regenerative Institute<br />
      45 Essex Street, Suite 202<br />
      Millburn, NJ, 07041
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

